Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露妮你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这可真是美如画啊 勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果打算娶菲丽希亚的话 可不能沾花惹草哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 我在故乡已经有喜欢的人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 你要是敢惹哭我妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着受死吧
